  {
    "Namespace": "",
    "Key": "7CA18BA44C6FA098F08B3CBB77D2B611",
    "Hash": 2875677918,
    "SourceString": "Intro:\r\nYou start at the story Intro Level. Highly recommended for your first play-through. \r\n\r\nObservatory:\r\nYou start at the Observatory, your first port-of-call in the main story.\r\n\r\nRandom:\r\nYou start in a semi-safe location on a random location in the southern zone.",
